+<http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Lexicon/NamedRockUnit/BLST> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Oilshale. Stratified bedrock. Occurs offshore. Deposited during the Kimmeridgian Age (Jurassic Period) (154.8-149.2 Ma BP)."@en .
+<http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Lexicon/NamedRockUnit/BROR> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Bituminous mudstone with subsidiary sandstone and silty sandstone. Stratified bedrock. Occurs onshore. Deposited during the Callovian Age (Jurassic Period) (165.3-161.5 Ma BP)."@en .
+<http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Lexicon/NamedRockUnit/MLP> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Obsolete name. Stratified bedrock. Occurs onshore. Deposited during the Bajocian Age (Jurassic Period) (170.9-168.2 Ma BP)."@en .
+<http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Lexicon/NamedRockUnit/BKML> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Blackmires Limestone Bed"@en .
+<http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Lexicon/NamedRockUnit/BLST> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Blackstone Bed (Jurassic)"@en .
+<http://data.bgs.ac.uk/id/Lexicon/NamedRockUnit/MLP> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Millepore Bed [Obsolete]"@en .
